Package Downloads

Daniel Turek

 

Data downloaded from CRAN, the Comprehensive R Archive Network, 19 May, 2021.

Green lines display LOWESS [1,2] smoothed curves.

 

suppressMessages(library(cranlogs))
suppressMessages(library(gplots))

df <- data.frame(
    pkgs = c('nimble', 'MATA', 'basicMCMCplots', 'BayesNSGP', 'nimbleEcology', 'nimbleSCR', 'nimbleSMC'),
    ymax = c(200, 80, 80, 40, 40, 30, 30)
)

from <- '2018-01-01'

downloads <- cranlogs::cran_downloads(df$pkgs, from = from, to = Sys.Date())

for(i in 1:nrow(df)) {
    count <- downloads[downloads$package == df$pkgs[i], ]$count
    date <- downloads[downloads$package == df$pkgs[i], ]$date
    plot(count ~ date, main = df$pkgs[i], ylim = c(0, df$ymax[i]),
         type = 'l', xlab = 'Date', ylab = 'Daily Downloads')
    ind <- min(which(count > 0)) : length(count)
    smoothed <- gplots::lowess(count[ind] ~ as.numeric(date[ind]), f = 1)
    lines(x = smoothed$x, y = smoothed$y, col = 'green', lwd = 3)
}

 

[1] Cleveland, William S. (1979). Robust locally weighted regression and smoothing scatterplots. Journal of the American Statistical Association, 74(368), 829-836.

[2] Cleveland, William S. (1981). LOWESS: A program for smoothing scatterplots by robust locally weighted regression. The American Statistician, 35(1): 54.
